---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<section
  class="nt-grain nt-grain-dark nt-hex-pattern"
  style="
    background: var(--nt-gradient-dark);
    padding: var(--nt-space-3xl) var(--nt-space-md);
    min-height: 88vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  "
  aria-label="Presentación"
>
  <div
    style="
      max-width: var(--nt-container);
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    "
  >
    <div class="hero-grid">

      <!-- Columna izquierda: texto -->
      <div>
        <!-- Eyebrow: keyword local -->
        <p
          style="
            font-family: var(--nt-font-ui);
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.14em;
            color: var(--nt-color-green-400);
            margin-bottom: var(--nt-space-md);
          "
        >
          Nutricionista en Asturias · Atención online para toda España
        </p>

        <!-- H1 — propuesta de valor directa -->
        <h1
          style="
            font-family: var(--nt-font-display);
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.25rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -0.025em;
            color: var(--nt-color-stone-50);
            margin-bottom: var(--nt-space-lg);
          "
        >
          La salud que construyes,<br />
          <em style="font-style: italic; color: var(--nt-color-earth-400)">no la dieta que aguantas.</em>
        </h1>

        <!-- Descripción con keywords semánticas -->
        <p
          style="
            font-family: var(--nt-font-body);
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.75vw, 1.1875rem);
            line-height: 1.75;
            color: var(--nt-color-stone-300);
            max-width: 38rem;
            margin-bottom: var(--nt-space-xl);
          "
        >
          En Nutroteca trabajamos los tres pilares de tu salud de forma coordinada:
          <strong style="color: var(--nt-color-stone-200); font-weight: 600">nutrición clínica</strong>,
          <strong style="color: var(--nt-color-stone-200); font-weight: 600">entrenamiento funcional</strong> y
          <strong style="color: var(--nt-color-stone-200); font-weight: 600">equilibrio emocional</strong>.
          No es una dieta. Es un cambio real, sostenible y sin atajos.
        </p>

        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--nt-space-md); align-items: center">
          <a
            href={`${base}/contacto`}
            style="
              display: inline-flex;
              align-items: center;
              background: var(--nt-color-stone-50);
              color: var(--nt-color-green-900);
              font-family: var(--nt-font-ui);
              font-weight: 600;
              font-size: 0.9375rem;
              padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
              border-radius: 3px;
              text-decoration: none;
            "
          >
            Primera consulta gratuita
          </a>
          <a
            href={`${base}/metodologia`}
            style="
              display: inline-flex;
              align-items: center;
              gap: 0.375rem;
              color: var(--nt-color-stone-300);
              font-family: var(--nt-font-ui);
              font-weight: 500;
              font-size: 0.9375rem;
              text-decoration: none;
            "
          >
            Conoce la metodología →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Prueba social mínima -->
        <div
          style="
            margin-top: var(--nt-space-2xl);
            padding-top: var(--nt-space-lg);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: var(--nt-space-lg);
          "
        >
          {[
            { num: '3',      label: 'pilares integrados' },
            { num: '100%',   label: 'personalizado' },
            { num: '0€',     label: 'primera consulta' },
          ].map(({ num, label }) => (
            <div>
              <p style="font-family: var(--nt-font-display); font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--nt-color-stone-50); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.25rem">
                {num}
              </p>
              <p style="font-family: var(--nt-font-ui); font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--nt-color-stone-400)">
                {label}
              </p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Columna derecha: foto del equipo -->
      <div class="hero-image-col" aria-hidden="true">
        <div
          style="
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            min-height: 480px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
          "
        >
          <!-- Placeholder foto equipo -->
          <div
            style="
              width: 100%;
              height: 100%;
              background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
              display: flex;
              flex-direction: column;
              align-items: center;
              justify-content: center;
              gap: 1rem;
              padding: 2rem;
              text-align: center;
            "
          >
            <!-- Icono cámara -->
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2)">
              <path d="M23 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4"/>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <p style="font-family: var(--nt-font-ui); font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 500; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); margin-bottom: 0.375rem">
                Foto del equipo
              </p>
              <p style="font-family: var(--nt-font-ui); font-size: 0.6875rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); max-width: 18rem">
                José Miguel y Erika · Retrato profesional en consulta o exterior natural
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Etiqueta decorativa inferior -->
          <div
            style="
              position: absolute;
              bottom: 1.25rem;
              left: 1.25rem;
              right: 1.25rem;
              background: rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
              backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
              border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
              border-radius: 3px;
              padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
              display: flex;
              align-items: center;
              gap: 0.75rem;
            "
          >
            <div
              style="
                width: 2.25rem;
                height: 2.25rem;
                border-radius: 50%;
                background: var(--nt-color-green-700);
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                flex-shrink: 0;
                font-family: var(--nt-font-display);
                font-size: 0.75rem;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: white;
              "
            >
              NT
            </div>
            <div>
              <p style="font-family: var(--nt-font-ui); font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--nt-color-stone-100)">
                José Miguel & Erika
              </p>
              <p style="font-family: var(--nt-font-ui); font-size: 0.6875rem; color: var(--nt-color-stone-400)">
                Nutricionista · Enfermera deportiva
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--nt-space-2xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-image-col {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--nt-space-xl);
    }

    .hero-image-col {
      display: block;
      height: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
